---
import BuyButton from './BuyButton.astro';

const achievements = [
  {
    icon: "💻",
    text: "18 years across platforms",
    color: "#FFD600"
  },
  {
    icon: "🧩",
    text: "Built systems, products, and UX",
    color: "#4A90E2"
  },
  {
    icon: "📖",
    text: "Real experience, not guru theory",
    color: "#2ECC71"
  }
];

const milestones = [
  "Shipping features nobody needed",
  "Endless sprint reviews",
  "Optimizing other people's vision",
  "Waiting for someone to say yes",
  "Building for hours, earning once"
];
---

<section id="about-author" class="relative py-24 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Gradient background matching site palette -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#FFF7E6] via-[#FFFBF2] to-[#FFF0D6]"></div>
  <!-- Halftone overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-halftone opacity-5 pointer-events-none mix-blend-multiply"></div>

  <!-- Floating emojis -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-[8%] left-[6%] text-5xl animate-float-a">✨</div>
    <div class="absolute top-[15%] right-[8%] text-5xl animate-float-b">🦥</div>
    <div class="absolute top-[45%] left-[3%] text-4xl animate-float-c">💡</div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-[20%] right-[5%] text-5xl animate-float-a">💫</div>
    <div class="absolute top-[60%] right-[18%] text-4xl animate-float-b">🧩</div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-[10%] left-[12%] text-4xl animate-float-c">🎯</div>
    <div class="absolute top-[30%] right-[35%] text-3xl animate-float-a">⭐</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Top border -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-0.5 bg-black"></div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left Column: Story Content -->
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center relative">

        <div class="inline-block bg-[#FFD600] border-2 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0_#000] rounded-2xl px-5 py-2 transform -rotate-2 mb-6 self-start">
          <p class="text-lg font-black text-[#1B1B3D]">The Person Behind This</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-[#1B1B3D] mb-8 transform rotate-1 leading-tight" style="font-family:'Bangers',cursive; letter-spacing:0.03em;">
          Built by Someone Who Has Done It 🦥
        </h2>

        <!-- Achievement Cards -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
          {achievements.map((achievement) => (
            <div class="bg-white border-2 border-black rounded-xl shadow-[4px_4px_0_#000] p-4 transform hover:scale-105 hover:-rotate-2 transition-all duration-300 text-center">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-3 flex items-center justify-center text-xl rounded-full border-2 border-black" style={`background: ${achievement.color}`}>
                {achievement.icon}
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold text-[#1B1B3D]">{achievement.text}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        
        <!-- Story Quote -->
        <div class="bg-[#FFD600]/40 border-2 border-black rounded-2xl shadow-[4px_4px_0_#000] px-6 py-4 transform rotate-1 mb-8">
          <p class="text-xl italic text-[#1B1B3D]">
            "I'm Remi. I've spent 18 years working in software development across multiple platforms, building products, systems, and user experiences used by real people."
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Story Content -->
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-[#1B1B3D]">
          <p>
            Those years taught me one thing that stuck: the best systems do the heavy work for you. Same idea here. Back then, a lot of days looked like this:
          </p>
          
          <!-- Milestone List -->
          <div class="bg-white/70 border-2 border-black rounded-xl shadow-[3px_3px_0_#000] p-6">
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              {milestones.map((milestone) => (
                <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <div class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#FF4D4D] border-2 border-black flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black text-xs">
                    ×
                  </div>
                  <span class="font-medium">{milestone}</span>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <p>
            Somewhere along the way it clicked: I'd spent almost two decades building products and systems for other people. It felt right to build something of my own.
          </p>
          
          <div class="bg-[#E3F2FF] border-2 border-black rounded-2xl shadow-[4px_4px_0_#000] px-6 py-4 transform -rotate-1">
            <p class="font-bold text-[#1B1B3D]">
              Strategic Sloth is the result of that shift. Simple systems, honest guides, and the freedom to work on your own terms.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Callout Box -->
        <div class="mt-8 bg-[#2C2D5D] border-2 border-black rounded-2xl shadow-[4px_4px_0_#000] p-6 transform hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-300">
          <p class="text-lg font-bold italic text-white">
            "Most of that time went into other people's roadmaps. Strategic Sloth is where I put what I learned into work that finally felt mine." 😴
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="mt-10 text-center">
          <div class="inline-block bg-[#FFD600] border-2 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0_#000] rounded-2xl px-6 py-3 transform rotate-1 mb-6">
            <p class="text-xl font-black text-[#1B1B3D]">Ready to start building something of your own? ✍️</p>
          </div>
          
          <BuyButton
            href="#get-started"
            variant="comic-primary"
            size="lg"
            text="Join the Freedom Movement →"
            class="comic-button bg-white text-black hover:bg-comic-accent hover:text-black transform hover:scale-105 hover:-rotate-2 transition-all duration-300"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Right Column: Photo with hover crossfade -->
      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <div class="relative inline-block">
          <!-- Shadow layer tied to image size -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 translate-x-3 translate-y-3 bg-black rounded-2xl -z-10"></div>
          <!-- Photo card with crossfade -->
          <div class="photo-card relative bg-[#FFD600] border-4 border-black rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transform hover:-rotate-1 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300">
            <!-- Illustration (default visible) -->
            <img
              src="/images/remi-illustration.webp"
              alt="Remi, founder of Strategic Sloth"
              class="photo-illustration w-full h-auto object-cover block"
              width="600"
              height="780"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
            />
            <!-- Real photo (fades in on hover) -->
            <img
              src="/images/remi-photo.webp"
              alt="Remi, founder of Strategic Sloth"
              class="photo-real absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-500"
              width="600"
              height="780"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
            />
            <!-- Status bubble -->
            <div class="absolute bottom-4 right-4 bg-white border-2 border-black rounded-2xl shadow-[3px_3px_0_#000] px-4 py-2 transform rotate-2 animate-float-b">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#2ECC71] animate-pulse border border-black"></div>
                <p class="text-sm font-black text-[#1B1B3D]">Building in the background 🦥</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Floating decorative emoji around photo -->
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 text-4xl animate-float-a pointer-events-none">✨</div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 text-3xl animate-float-c pointer-events-none">💡</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Bottom border -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-0.5 bg-black"></div>
</section>

<style>
  .bg-halftone {
    background-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 24px 24px;
  }

  /* Crossfade on hover */
  .photo-card:hover .photo-real {
    opacity: 1;
  }
  .photo-card:hover .photo-illustration {
    opacity: 0;
  }
  .photo-illustration {
    transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
  }

  @keyframes float-a {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); opacity: 0.8; }
    50% { transform: translateY(-18px) rotate(8deg); opacity: 1; }
  }
  @keyframes float-b {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(-3deg); opacity: 0.8; }
    50% { transform: translateY(-14px) rotate(5deg); opacity: 1; }
  }
  @keyframes float-c {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(4deg); opacity: 0.7; }
    50% { transform: translateY(-22px) rotate(-4deg); opacity: 1; }
  }

  .animate-float-a { animation: float-a 6s ease-in-out infinite; }
  .animate-float-b { animation: float-b 8s ease-in-out infinite; }
  .animate-float-c { animation: float-c 7s ease-in-out infinite; }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .animate-float-a, .animate-float-b, .animate-float-c { animation: none; }
  }
</style>

